dct_title_s: 1928 September 30th state highway system of Indiana
dct_description_sm: Caption title: Sub-district & road section map. Shows roads by surface and composition type as well as official highway markers, boundaries and headquarters for districts and sub-districts, and construction status. Appears in Report of the Indiana State Highway Commission for the fiscal year ending September 30, 1928 / State Highway Commission. In Year book of the State of Indiana for 1928 / The Legislative Reference Bureau. Indianapolis : Wm. B. Burford, contractor for state printing and binding, 1929.
Imprint: [Indianapolis] : [Wm. B. Burford, contractor for state printing and binding], [1929]; Imprint: [Indianapolis] : [The Legislative Bureau], [1929]
Dimensions: 36 x 23 cm, on sheet 41 x 26 cm
